"title": "8227: discernment, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8227",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Discernment is given by God, through his Holy Spirit. It is received through God's word and through the insight of a renewed mind. Discerning believers seek to grow in their understanding and knowledge of God's truth.</p>\n<h2>Discernment as sound judgment</h2>\n<h3>Judging the right course</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:21\">PRO 15:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:9-Phil1:10\">PHP 1:9–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:21-Prov3:23\">PRO 3:21–3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:8-Prov8:9\">PRO 8:8–8:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:21\">PRO 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:12\">PRO 11:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:1\">PRO 18:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:30\">PRO 24:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:9\">HOS 14:9</a></p>\n<h3>Distinguishing good from evil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:17\">2SA 14:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:22\">GEN 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:30\">JOB 6:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:3-Job34:4\">JOB 34:3–34:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:15\">ISA 7:15</a></p>\n<h3>Distinguishing holy from common</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:10\">LEV 10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:47\">LEV 11:47</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:26\">EZK 22:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:23\">EZK 44:23</a></p>\n<h3>Seeing through outward appearances</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:11\">PRO 28:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:7\">1SA 16:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:3\">ISA 11:3</a></p>\n<h3>Understanding the significance of events</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:29-Deut32:30\">DEU 32:29–32:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:32\">1CH 12:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:13\">EST 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:32-Matt24:33\">MAT 24:32–24:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:28-Mark13:29\">MRK 13:28–13:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:54-Luke12:56\">LUK 12:54–12:56</a></p>\n<h3>Exercising judgment to rule</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:9\">1KI 3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:14-Prov8:16\">PRO 8:14–8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:2\">PRO 28:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:16\">PRO 28:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:5\">JER 23:5</a></p>\n<h2>Discernment as insight into spiritual realities</h2>\n<h3>Distinguishing between spirits</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:10\">1CO 12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:19-1Kgs22:23\">1KI 22:19–22:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:18-2Chr18:22\">2CH 18:18–18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1\">1TI 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1-1John4:3\">1JN 4:1–4:3</a></p>\n<h3>Discerning true and false prophecy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:1-Deut13:3\">DEU 13:1–13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:21-Deut18:22\">DEU 18:21–18:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:29\">1CO 14:29</a></p>\n<h2>Characteristics of discerning people</h2>\n<h3>The discerning grow in wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:5\">PRO 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:9\">PRO 9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:14\">PRO 10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:6\">PRO 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:14\">PRO 15:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:24\">PRO 17:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:15\">PRO 18:15</a></p>\n<h3>The discerning accept rebuke</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:10\">PRO 17:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:25\">PRO 19:25</a></p>\n<h3>The discerning keep God's law</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:12\">1CH 22:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:34\">PSA 119:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:7\">PRO 28:7</a></p>\n<h2>The source of discernment</h2>\n<h3>Discernment is given by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:21\">DAN 2:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:10\">PRO 9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:27-Dan2:28\">DAN 2:27–2:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:12-1Cor2:15\">1CO 2:12–2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Discernment through God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:14\">HEB 5:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7\">PSA 19:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:98-Ps119:100\">PSA 119:98–119:100</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:130\">PSA 119:130</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:18\">ROM 2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Discernment through a renewed mind</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33\">JER 31:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:16\">1CO 2:16</a></p>\n<h3>Asking for discernment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:66\">PSA 119:66</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:27\">PSA 119:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:125\">PSA 119:125</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5\">JAS 1:5</a></p>",
